    public interface VelocityStructure
extends java.io.Serializable
    Structure information for computing travel time.
    関連項目:

      • kTurningR

        double kTurningR(double rayParameter)
        The turning radius is r with which qτ = 0.

        r = p(N/ρ)1/2* r = p(N/ρ)1/2

        パラメータ:
        rayParameter - ray parameter
        戻り値:
        [km] the K turning radius for the raypath or Double.NaN if there is no valid R. The radius must be in the outercore.
        関連項目:
        "Woodhouse (1981)"

      • shTurningR

        double shTurningR(double rayParameter)

        パラメータ:

        戻り値:
